			<title>Activity- Web Tour of Sound-Annotated Pictures</title>
			<link>https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/index.php?option=com_content__view=article__id=110__catid=17__Itemid=53</link>
			<description><![CDATA[<p align="left">The Web Tour of Sound-Annotated Pictures is a set of 34 images that have been enhanced with sound&nbsp;such that regions of the photographs are identified and then associated with a sound. The user can explore the regions via mouse or keyboard, listening to the sounds separately or together and also receiving textual descriptions for the various regions or the image as a whole.</p><ul><li><div align="left"><a href="http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/fr/dossiers/SONS_FR" target="_blank">French Version</a></div></li><li><div align="left"><a href="http://www.musee-mccord.qc.ca/fr/dossiers/SONS_EN" target="_blank">English Version</a></div></li></ul><p align="left">{mosimage}&nbsp;</p>]]></description>
